data.description: Welcome Home to 1.9 acres In Mill Creek II in Orange County ~ 3 Bedrooms & 2 Baths ~ Front Porch 17x6 ~ Back Deck 10x12 ~ Storage Building 16x16 ~ Vaulted Ceiling in Living Room has Ceiling Fan, Gas Log Fireplace ~ Galley Kitchen with Stainless Appliances & Pantry, Dining Area ~ Primary Bedroom has Vaulted Ceiling, Ceiling Fan & fresh paint, Open to double vanity, Separate Bathtub and Shower, Walk in Closet ~ Great area in front yard for a garden ~ New flooring is needed in Primary Bedroom ~ Extra Tile is in Storage Building to finish off the hallway~ $5000 Flooring Allowance with Acceptable Offer~ Septic Pumped 2020~ HIGHEST OFFERS PLEASE SUBMIT BY MONDAY, 2/19 at 5PM; Seller reserves the right to accept an offer before deadline.
